-600 hover:bg-brand-50 block px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-base font-medium transition-all\\\"> Privacy </a> <a href=\\\"/terms\\\" class=\\\"text-warm-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50 block px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-base font-medium transition-all\\\"> Terms </a> </div> </div> </nav> <script type=\\\"module\\\">const e=document.getElementById(\\\"mobile-menu-button\\\"),t=document.getElementById(\\\"mobile-menu\\\"),n=document.getElementById(\\\"menu-icon-closed\\\"),d=document.getElementById(\\\"menu-icon-open\\\");e&&t&&n&&d&&e.addEventListener(\\\"click\\\",()=>{const o=e.getAttribute(\\\"aria-expanded\\\")===\\\"true\\\";t.classList.toggle(\\\"hidden\\\"),n.classList.toggle(\\\"hidden\\\"),d.classList.toggle(\\\"hidden\\\"),e.setAttribute(\\\"aria-expanded\\\",(!o).toString())});</script> <!-- Header --> <div class=\\\"relative overflow-hidden\\\"> <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-50 via-cream-50 to-brand-100/40\\\"></div> <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-72 h-72 bg-brand-200/15 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/3 translate-x-1/4\\\"></div> <div class=\\\"relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-14 sm:py-18 text-center\\\"> <h1 class=\\\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-3\\\"> Frequently Asked Questions </h1> <p class=\\\"text-warm-400 text-sm max-w-lg mx-auto\\\"> If you encounter any unsolvable problems or have other feedback, please feel free to email us at: hello@catonchair.app </p> </div> </div> <main class=\\\"flex-grow max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16 w-full -mt-2\\\"> <div class=\\\"space-y-4\\\"> <!-- Question 1 --> <details class=\\\"group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/50 shadow-sm shadow-warm-200/20 overflow-hidden\\\"> <summary class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 md:p-8 select-none\\\"> <h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-brand-800 pr-4\\\"> How to enable Whitelist Mode? </h2> <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-brand-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"> <path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\\\"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class=\\\"px-6 pb-6 md:px-8 md:pb-8 -mt-2\\\"> <div class=\\\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\\\"> <strong>Whitelist Mode</strong> can be enabled in the <strong>Focus Mode</strong> within Settings. When selecting apps, avoid selecting entire categories. If an entire category is selected, the whitelist mode will become invalid. If a category contains only one app, or if all apps in a category are selected, the category will be automatically selected. In this case, downloading another app in that category can solve the problem. </div> </div> </details> <!-- Question 2 --> <details class=\\\"group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/50 shadow-sm shadow-warm-200/20 overflow-hidden\\\"> <summary class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 md:p-8 select-none\\\"> <h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-brand-800 pr-4\\\"> Why can some apps still be used even if they are not on the whitelist? </h2> <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-brand-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"> <path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\\\"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class=\\\"px-6 pb-6 md:px-8 md:pb-8 -mt-2\\\"> <div class=\\\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\\\"> If you have set <strong>Screen Time</strong> limits for an app and then choose to <strong>\\\"Ignore Limit\\\"</strong> for that day, the app will no longer be restricted by <strong>Cat on Chair</strong>. </div> </div> </details> <!-- Question 3 (Family Sharing) --> <details class=\\\"group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/50 shadow-sm shadow-warm-200/20 overflow-hidden\\\"> <summary class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 md:p-8 select-none\\\"> <h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-brand-800 pr-4\\\"> How do I share with family members after purchasing a Family Sharing membership? </h2> <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-brand-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"> <path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\\\"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class=\\\"px-6 pb-6 md:px-8 md:pb-8 -mt-2\\\"> <div class=\\\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\\\"> Since our Family Sharing is built on Apple's <strong>iCloud Family</strong> system, all members must be in the same iCloud Family. Annual family subscriptions share automatically with family members. For <strong>Lifetime Family</strong> membership, you need to enable <strong>\\\"Share My Purchases\\\"</strong>. We recommend sharing with family members or close friends you know privately. Please be careful with your personal and financial security if sharing with strangers. </div> </div> </details> <!-- Question 4 (Android) --> <details class=\\\"group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/50 shadow-sm shadow-warm-200/20 overflow-hidden\\\"> <summary class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 md:p-8 select-none\\\"> <h2 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-brand-800 pr-4\\\"> Is there an Android version? </h2> <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-brand-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"> <path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\\\"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class=\\\"px-6 pb-6 md:px-8 md:pb-8 -mt-2\\\"> <div class=\\\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\\\"> Currently, our resources are limited, and we cannot support Android development. We plan to focus on perfecting the <strong>Apple ecosystem</strong> first, such as Apple Watch and Mac versions, before considering an Android version. </div> </div> </details> </div> </main> <footer class=\\\"bg-cream-100/80 border-t border-warm-200/50 mt-auto\\\"> <div class=\\\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10\\\"> <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8\\\"> <!-- Brand --> <div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\"> <h3 class=\\\"font-title text-lg text-brand-700\\\"> Cat on Chair </h3> <p class=\\\"text-sm text-warm-500 leading-relaxed\\\"> Enjoy a cozy, playful focus experience. The cat isn’t there to “supervise”; they’re sharing the moment with you. </p> </div> <!-- Quick Links --> <div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\"> <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-semibold text-warm-400 uppercase tracking-widest\\\"> Home </h4> <div class=\\\"space-y-1.5\\\"> <a href=\\\"/en\\\" class=\\\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\\\"> Home </a> <a href=\\\"/en/claim-pro-event\\\" class=\\\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\\\"> Focus Challenge </a> <a href=\\\"/en/faq\\\" class=\\\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\\\"> FAQ </a> <a href=\\\"/en/privacy\\\" class=\\\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\\\"> Privacy </a> <a href=\\\"/en/terms\\\" class=\\\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\\\"> Terms </a> </div> </div> <!-- Contact --> <div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\"> <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-semibold text-warm-400 uppercase tracking-widest\\\"> Contact </h4> <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"> <a href=\\\"mailto:hello@catonchair.app\\\" class=\\\"inline-flex items-center text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\\\"> <svg class=\\\"w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-brand-400\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"> <path stroke-linecap=\\\