over:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all\"> Privacy </a> <a href=\"/terms\" class=\"text-warm-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all\"> Terms </a> </div> <!-- Mobile Menu Button --> <div class=\"flex items-center md:hidden\"> <button type=\"button\" id=\"mobile-menu-button\" class=\"text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-50 transition-colors focus:outline-none\" aria-controls=\"mobile-menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\"> <span class=\"sr-only\">Open main menu</span> <svg class=\"h-5 w-5 block\" id=\"menu-icon-closed\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3.75 6.75h16.5M3.75 12h16.5m-16.5 5.25h16.5\"></path> </svg> <svg class=\"h-5 w-5 hidden\" id=\"menu-icon-open\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"></path> </svg> </button> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Mobile Menu --> <div class=\"hidden md:hidden absolute top-14 left-0 w-full bg-cream-50/95 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-warm-200/60 shadow-lg shadow-warm-200/20 z-50\" id=\"mobile-menu\"> <div class=\"px-3 pt-2 pb-3 space-y-0.5\"> <a href=\"/\" class=\"text-warm-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50 block px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-base font-medium transition-all\"> Home </a> <a href=\"/faq\" class=\"text-warm-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50 block px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-base font-medium transition-all\"> FAQ </a> <a href=\"/privacy\" class=\"text-warm-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50 block px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-base font-medium transition-all\"> Privacy </a> <a href=\"/terms\" class=\"text-warm-600 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50 block px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-base font-medium transition-all\"> Terms </a> </div> </div> </nav> <script type=\"module\">const e=document.getElementById(\"mobile-menu-button\"),t=document.getElementById(\"mobile-menu\"),n=document.getElementById(\"menu-icon-closed\"),d=document.getElementById(\"menu-icon-open\");e&&t&&n&&d&&e.addEventListener(\"click\",()=>{const o=e.getAttribute(\"aria-expanded\")===\"true\";t.classList.toggle(\"hidden\"),n.classList.toggle(\"hidden\"),d.classList.toggle(\"hidden\"),e.setAttribute(\"aria-expanded\",(!o).toString())});</script> <!-- Header --> <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden\"> <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-50 via-cream-50 to-brand-100/40\"></div> <div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-72 h-72 bg-brand-200/15 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/3 translate-x-1/4\"></div> <div class=\"relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-14 sm:py-18 text-center\"> <h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-3\"> Frequently Asked Questions </h1> <p class=\"text-warm-400 text-sm max-w-lg mx-auto\"> If you encounter any unsolvable problems or have other feedback, please feel free to email us at: hello@catonchair.app </p> </div> </div> <main class=\"flex-grow max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16 w-full -mt-2\"> <div class=\"space-y-4\"> <!-- Question 1 --> <details class=\"group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/50 shadow-sm shadow-warm-200/20 overflow-hidden\"> <summary class=\"flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 md:p-8 select-none\"> <h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-brand-800 pr-4\"> How to enable Whitelist Mode? </h2> <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-brand-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"> <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 md:px-8 md:pb-8 -mt-2\"> <div class=\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\"> <strong>Whitelist Mode</strong> can be enabled in the <strong>Focus Mode</strong> within Settings. When selecting apps, avoid selecting entire categories. If an entire category is selected, the whitelist mode will become invalid. If a category contains only one app, or if all apps in a category are selected, the category will be automatically selected. In this case, downloading another app in that category can solve the problem. </div> </div> </details> <!-- Question 2 --> <details class=\"group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/50 shadow-sm shadow-warm-200/20 overflow-hidden\"> <summary class=\"flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 md:p-8 select-none\"> <h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-brand-800 pr-4\"> Why can some apps still be used even if they are not on the whitelist? </h2> <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-brand-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"> <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 md:px-8 md:pb-8 -mt-2\"> <div class=\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\"> If you have set <strong>Screen Time</strong> limits for an app and then choose to <strong>\"Ignore Limit\"</strong> for that day, the app will no longer be restricted by <strong>Cat on Chair</strong>. </div> </div> </details> <!-- Question 3 (Family Sharing) --> <details class=\"group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/50 shadow-sm shadow-warm-200/20 overflow-hidden\"> <summary class=\"flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 md:p-8 select-none\"> <h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-brand-800 pr-4\"> How do I share with family members after purchasing a Family Sharing membership? </h2> <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-brand-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"> <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 md:px-8 md:pb-8 -mt-2\"> <div class=\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\"> Since our Family Sharing is built on Apple's <strong>iCloud Family</strong> system, all members must be in the same iCloud Family. Annual family subscriptions share automatically with family members. For <strong>Lifetime Family</strong> membership, you need to enable <strong>\"Share My Purchases\"</strong>. We recommend sharing with family members or close friends you know privately. Please be careful with your personal and financial security if sharing with strangers. </div> </div> </details> <!-- Question 4 (Android) --> <details class=\"group bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/50 shadow-sm shadow-warm-200/20 overflow-hidden\"> <summary class=\"flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer p-6 md:p-8 select-none\"> <h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-brand-800 pr-4\"> Is there an Android version? </h2> <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-brand-400 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"> <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path> </svg> </summary> <div class=\"px-6 pb-6 md:px-8 md:pb-8 -mt-2\"> <div class=\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\"> Currently, our resources are limited, and we cannot support Android development. We plan to focus on perfecting the <strong>Apple ecosystem</strong> first, such as Apple Watch and Mac versions, before considering an Android version. </div> </div> </details> </div> </main> <footer class=\"bg-cream-100/80 border-t border-warm-200/50 mt-auto\"> <div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10\"> <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"> <!-- Brand --> <div class=\"space-y-3\"> <h3 class=\"font-title text-lg text-brand-700\"> Cat on Chair </h3> <p class=\"text-sm text-warm-500 leading-relaxed\"> Enjoy a cozy, playful focus experience. The cat isn’t there to “supervise”; they’re sharing the moment with you. </p> </div> <!-- Quick Links --> <div class=\"space-y-3\"> <h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-warm-400 uppercase tracking-widest\"> Home </h4> <div class=\"space-y-1.5\"> <a href=\"/en\" class=\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> Home </a> <a href=\"/en/claim-pro-event\" class=\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> Focus Challenge </a> <a href=\"/en/faq\" class=\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> FAQ </a> <a href=\"/en/privacy\" class=\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> Privacy </a> <a href=\"/en/terms\" class=\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> Terms </a> </div> </div> <!-- Contact --> <div class=\"space-y-3\"> <h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-warm-400 uppercase tracking-widest\"> Contact </h4> <div class=\"space-y-2\"> <a href=\"mailto:hello@catonchair.app\" class=\"inline-flex items-center text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-brand-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"> <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z\"></path> </svg>\nhello@catonchair.app\n</a> <p class=\"text-xs text-warm-400\"> Contact Us </p> </div> </div> <!-- Language --> <div class=\"space-y-3\"> <h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-warm-400 uppercase tracking-widest\"> Language </h4> <div class=\"flex items-center\"> <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\" id=\"language-switcher\"> <button data-locale=\"en\" class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium transition-all bg-brand-100 text-brand-700\">\nEN\n</button> <span class=\"text-warm-300 text-xs\">|</span> <button data-locale=\"zh\" class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium transition-all text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50\">\n简体\n</button> <span class=\"text-warm-300 text-xs\">|</span> <button data-locale=\"zh-Hant\" class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium transition-all text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50\">\n繁體\n</button> </div> <script type=\"module\">document.getElementById(\"language-switcher\")?.addEventListener(\"click\",n=>{const e=n.target;if(e.tagName===\"BUTTON\"){const t=e.getAttribute(\"data-locale\");if(t){const a=window.location.pathname.replace(/^\\/(en|zh-Hant|zh)(?=\\/|$)/,\"\"),c=t===\"en\"?a||\"/\":`/${t}${a||\"/\"}`;window.location.href=c}}});</script> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Copyright --> <div class=\"mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-warm-200/50\"> <p class=\"text-xs text-warm-400 text-center\"> © 2025 Cat On Desk Design Inc. All rights reserved. </p> </div> </div> </footer> </div>  </div> </body></html>","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
