-200/20 p-6 md:p-8\"> <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-5\">📱How to Join</h2> <ol class=\"space-y-4\"> <li class=\"flex gap-4\"> <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-brand-100 text-brand-600 text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5\">1</span> <p class=\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\">Open the <strong>Cat on Chair</strong> app and start your focus session.</p> </li> <li class=\"flex gap-4\"> <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-brand-100 text-brand-600 text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5\">2</span> <p class=\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\">Take a screenshot, record a video, or share your thoughts — show us your most creative way of using <strong>Cat on Chair</strong>. (Video: no less than 10 secondss. Photos: No less than 3 photos that have app interface in it)</p> </li> <li class=\"flex gap-4\"> <span class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-brand-100 text-brand-600 text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mt-0.5\">3</span> <p class=\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\">Post on <strong>Threads / Instagram / TikTok</strong> with the hashtags: <strong>#CatOnChair #CatFocusChallenge #iphoneapp #adhdtips</strong></p> </li> </ol> </section> <!-- Rewards --> <section class=\"bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/50 shadow-sm shadow-warm-200/20 p-6 md:p-8\"> <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-5\">🎁 Membership Rewards Based on Likes</h2> <div class=\"grid gap-3\"> <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-xl bg-brand-50/60 border border-brand-100/50\"> <span class=\"text-warm-600 font-medium\">10+ likes</span> <span class=\"text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm bg-brand-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Free 30-day membership</span> </div> <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-xl bg-brand-50/60 border border-brand-100/50\"> <span class=\"text-warm-600 font-medium\">50+ likes</span> <span class=\"text-brand-600 font-semibold text-sm bg-brand-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Free 90-day membership</span> </div> <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-xl bg-brand-50/80 border border-brand-200/50\"> <span class=\"text-warm-600 font-medium\">100+ likes</span> <span class=\"text-brand-700 font-bold text-sm bg-brand-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Free 365-day membership</span> </div> </div> </section> <!-- Redeem --> <section class=\"bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/50 shadow-sm shadow-warm-200/20 p-6 md:p-8\"> <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-5\">📌 How to Redeem</h2> <ul class=\"space-y-3\"> <li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start\"> <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-brand-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"> <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z\"></path> </svg> <p class=\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\">Email us your post screenshot, your profile screenshot, and the link to: <strong>hello@catonchair.app</strong></p> </li> <li class=\"flex gap-3 items-start\"> <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-brand-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"> <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path> </svg> <p class=\"text-warm-600 leading-relaxed\">We’ll send you your redeemable membership code within 72 hours.</p> </li> </ul> </section> <!-- Pro Tips --> <section class=\"bg-brand-50/60 rounded-2xl border border-brand-100/60 p-6 md:p-8\"> <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-brand-700 mb-4\">🎯 Pro Tips</h3> <ul class=\"space-y-2.5\"> <li class=\"flex gap-2.5 items-start text-sm text-brand-800/80\"> <span class=\"text-brand-400 mt-0.5\">&#8226;</span> <span>Make sure your account is set to public so we can see your post.</span> </li> <li class=\"flex gap-2.5 items-start text-sm text-brand-800/80\"> <span class=\"text-brand-400 mt-0.5\">&#8226;</span> <span>Please do not edit your post after it’s been posted. If you want to make changes, please delete it and repost it.</span> </li> <li class=\"flex gap-2.5 items-start text-sm text-brand-800/80\"> <span class=\"text-brand-400 mt-0.5\">&#8226;</span> <span>Please do not delete your post after redeem the pro, we might take your membership away.</span> </li> <li class=\"flex gap-2.5 items-start text-sm text-brand-800/80\"> <span class=\"text-brand-400 mt-0.5\">&#8226;</span> <span>Each user can only redeem once, so make sure send your best post to get higher reward.</span> </li>  </ul> </section> <!-- Footer CTA --> <div class=\"text-center py-6\"> <p class=\"text-base font-medium text-brand-700\"> Become the most focused version of yourself! Start your focus journey today, share your progress, and let the world see your focus power </p> </div> </div> </main> <footer class=\"bg-cream-100/80 border-t border-warm-200/50 mt-auto\"> <div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10\"> <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"> <!-- Brand --> <div class=\"space-y-3\"> <h3 class=\"font-title text-lg text-brand-700\"> Cat on Chair </h3> <p class=\"text-sm text-warm-500 leading-relaxed\"> Enjoy a cozy, playful focus experience. The cat isn’t there to “supervise”; they’re sharing the moment with you. </p> </div> <!-- Quick Links --> <div class=\"space-y-3\"> <h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-warm-400 uppercase tracking-widest\"> Home </h4> <div class=\"space-y-1.5\"> <a href=\"/en\" class=\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> Home </a> <a href=\"/en/claim-pro-event\" class=\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> Focus Challenge </a> <a href=\"/en/faq\" class=\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> FAQ </a> <a href=\"/en/privacy\" class=\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> Privacy </a> <a href=\"/en/terms\" class=\"block text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> Terms </a> </div> </div> <!-- Contact --> <div class=\"space-y-3\"> <h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-warm-400 uppercase tracking-widest\"> Contact </h4> <div class=\"space-y-2\"> <a href=\"mailto:hello@catonchair.app\" class=\"inline-flex items-center text-sm text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 transition-colors\"> <svg class=\"w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-brand-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"> <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z\"></path> </svg>\nhello@catonchair.app\n</a> <p class=\"text-xs text-warm-400\"> Contact Us </p> </div> </div> <!-- Language --> <div class=\"space-y-3\"> <h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-warm-400 uppercase tracking-widest\"> Language </h4> <div class=\"flex items-center\"> <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\" id=\"language-switcher\"> <button data-locale=\"en\" class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium transition-all bg-brand-100 text-brand-700\">\nEN\n</button> <span class=\"text-warm-300 text-xs\">|</span> <button data-locale=\"zh\" class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium transition-all text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50\">\n简体\n</button> <span class=\"text-warm-300 text-xs\">|</span> <button data-locale=\"zh-Hant\" class=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium transition-all text-warm-500 hover:text-brand-600 hover:bg-brand-50\">\n繁體\n</button> </div> <script type=\"module\">document.getElementById(\"language-switcher\")?.addEventListener(\"click\",n=>{const e=n.target;if(e.tagName===\"BUTTON\"){const t=e.getAttribute(\"data-locale\");if(t){const a=window.location.pathname.replace(/^\\/(en|zh-Hant|zh)(?=\\/|$)/,\"\"),c=t===